<p><b>What is understanding the organization and its context?</b> The main goal of understanding the context of your organization is to identify the external and internal issues. Those issues have to be relevant to the goals and ambitions of your company. Every area of expertise, sector, market, or product family has its relevant issues that are affecting your organizational context.</p>
